Normal Operation (with OIFITS)

./oifits-sim -t ~/Projects/CHARA/simulator_info/target_epsAur.txt  -s ~/Projects/CHARA/simulator_info/MIRC_LowH.txt  -obs ~/Projects/CHARA/simulator_info/obs_epsAur.txt  -i ~/Projects/CHARA/simulator_info/MIRC.txt   -a ~/Projects/CHARA/simulator_info/CHARA.txt  -o /tmp/test.oifits

Debugging:

gdb ./oifits-sim
run -t ~/Projects/CHARA/simulator_info/target_epsAur.txt  -s ~/Projects/CHARA/simulator_info/MIRC_LowH.txt  -obs ~/Projects/CHARA/simulator_info/obs_epsAur.txt  -i ~/Projects/CHARA/simulator_info/MIRC.txt   -a ~/Projects/CHARA/simulator_info/CHARA.txt  -o /tmp/test.oifits


